1301				// Decoded under this psk but not a PROBE (DATA/PARITY carry no MAC, so
1302				// this may be a genuine PROBE from a later peer that cross-garbled into an
1303				// unauthenticated kind here). No binding authority: try the remaining psks
1304				// rather than aborting — a genuine unbound DATA/PARITY still never binds.
